lemma Simulation_Invariants_strengthen_post': assumes "Simulation_Invariants A B sim PA QA PB QB" "\<And> a b. PB a \<Longrightarrow> QB b \<Longrightarrow> B a b \<Longrightarrow> QB' b" "\<And> a. QB' a \<Longrightarrow> QB a" shows "Simulation_Invariants A B sim PA QA PB QB'"
using assms
by (auto simp add: Simulation_Invariants_def dest: rtranclpD)
